  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/5cfe9d690a1b94fd3549a2e45b652b95.avif?t=1743528407\" width=640 height=167 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Versus Purgatory is a micro-roguelike shoot-em-up with mind-bending gameplay in which you delve into a dungeon, controlling two characters at the same time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game takes ~2-3 hours on average to beat, with individual runs taking 10-15 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gamepad is strongly recommended!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/10ae9893d1efe698e96ece8f1a2a08d1.poster.avif?t=1743528407\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/10ae9893d1efe698e96ece8f1a2a08d1.webm?t=1743528407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/10ae9893d1efe698e96ece8f1a2a08d1.mp4?t=1743528407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don’t let the two characters fool you, this is a single-player game!</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot-em-up action! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Novel control scheme! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 unique weapons to discover! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ power-ups! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Millions of possible dungeons! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/IMG_0346.PNG?t=1743528407\" /></span>Versus Purgatory is a <i>randomly-generated action shooter roguelike</i>. Find wild and exciting new <i>weapons and power-ups</i> that change how you play. Discover secrets and fight your way to freedom. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/019495f8776032df9cd9acdbcfa2d8d5.poster.avif?t=1743528407\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/019495f8776032df9cd9acdbcfa2d8d5.webm?t=1743528407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/019495f8776032df9cd9acdbcfa2d8d5.mp4?t=1743528407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/3d5574ef7fa93abd03130bdfd133a0df.poster.avif?t=1743528407\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/3d5574ef7fa93abd03130bdfd133a0df.webm?t=1743528407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/3d5574ef7fa93abd03130bdfd133a0df.mp4?t=1743528407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/IMG_0347.PNG?t=1743528407\" /></span>Two spirits, an angel and a devil, were sentenced to Purgatory for their deviancy. Despite their hatred for one another, they must work together to <i>shoot, blast, and zap</i> their way out of the <i>ever-changing labyrinth</i> they've been trapped in. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/5cfe9d690a1b94fd3549a2e45b652b95.avif?t=1743528407\" width=640 height=167 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Versus Purgatory is a micro-roguelike shoot-em-up with mind-bending gameplay in which you delve into a dungeon, controlling two characters at the same time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game takes ~2-3 hours on average to beat, with individual runs taking 10-15 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gamepad is strongly recommended!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/10ae9893d1efe698e96ece8f1a2a08d1.poster.avif?t=1743528407\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/10ae9893d1efe698e96ece8f1a2a08d1.webm?t=1743528407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/10ae9893d1efe698e96ece8f1a2a08d1.mp4?t=1743528407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don’t let the two characters fool you, this is a single-player game!</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot-em-up action! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Novel control scheme! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 unique weapons to discover! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ power-ups! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Millions of possible dungeons! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/IMG_0346.PNG?t=1743528407\" /></span>Versus Purgatory is a <i>randomly-generated action shooter roguelike</i>. Find wild and exciting new <i>weapons and power-ups</i> that change how you play. Discover secrets and fight your way to freedom. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/019495f8776032df9cd9acdbcfa2d8d5.poster.avif?t=1743528407\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/019495f8776032df9cd9acdbcfa2d8d5.webm?t=1743528407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/019495f8776032df9cd9acdbcfa2d8d5.mp4?t=1743528407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/3d5574ef7fa93abd03130bdfd133a0df.poster.avif?t=1743528407\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/3d5574ef7fa93abd03130bdfd133a0df.webm?t=1743528407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/3d5574ef7fa93abd03130bdfd133a0df.mp4?t=1743528407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/IMG_0347.PNG?t=1743528407\" /></span>Two spirits, an angel and a devil, were sentenced to Purgatory for their deviancy. Despite their hatred for one another, they must work together to <i>shoot, blast, and zap</i> their way out of the <i>ever-changing labyrinth</i> they've been trapped in. </p>",
